The first specialized legal channel in Egypt and the Middle East, is a digital Channel, aims to enhance and support the legal culture in the MENA Region, highlight the potentials of innovation and creativity, activate the role of media, and to connect the legal community, through high quality media production services.

Law TV serves the legal society through introducing; 
1- social legal services for the public  ; 
2- Full Media Coverage of legal events and conferences, and finally; 
3- Private Advertising Services based on Smart Media Production.   

Law TV provides a full set of legal marketing services tailored for law firms, such as designing the firm's identity and building an extensive social media presence. We also offer other services, including media production, event management, digital marketing, website management, graphic and branding design, internal software systems, public relations, and business development & consultancy.
